    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/8c81a3a50da621f48db627b1a267533e.avif?t=1761052622\" width=640 height=100 /></span><strong>POLYGON</strong>是来自第1人称的战术多人队射击游戏。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用各种武器，你将在大型地图上与<strong>32名玩家</strong>战斗。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >胜任管理你的武器库和技能，你将带领你的球队取得胜利！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/7638211b8c414f2b738ed9a22e771c11.poster.avif?t=1761052622\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/7638211b8c414f2b738ed9a22e771c11.webm?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/7638211b8c414f2b738ed9a22e771c11.mp4?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在多达16名玩家的团队中进行激烈的PvP比赛。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >团队与你的朋友在一个小队采取团队游戏到一个新的水平！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/e9576659283cfaf2a08e4bf25ef587a2.poster.avif?t=1761052622\" width=600 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/e9576659283cfaf2a08e4bf25ef587a2.webm?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/e9576659283cfaf2a08e4bf25ef587a2.mp4?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >一个大型武器库可用-每个武器都有一个真正的原型！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >突击步枪，PDWs，机枪，神射手和狙击步枪之间进行选择, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >找到自己的打法。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/5530f700d9ded9756179a6e1d5ebaf08.poster.avif?t=1761052622\" width=600 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/5530f700d9ded9756179a6e1d5ebaf08.webm?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/5530f700d9ded9756179a6e1d5ebaf08.mp4?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >定制系统将帮助您根据您的需要定制武器。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >更换瞄准器，手柄，枪口装置和配件。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >此外，你可以解锁许多皮肤在战场上脱颖而出！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/58d04abfd590cf6f34681194492312fb.poster.avif?t=1761052622\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1241100/extras/58d04abfd590cf6f34681194492312fb.webm?t=1761052622\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在任何地点加入战斗：从宽敞的山谷到狭窄的地铁。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>不同的地图–不同的情况！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏正在不断改进。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用新的武器和技能改变战斗的结果。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >与朋友组队，探索新的地点。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发展</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直观的控制和直观的游戏玩法使游戏简单而有趣。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由于<strong>虚幻引擎5</strong>，多边形很容易在弱Pc上运行，并在现代计算机上显示其所有功能。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虚幻引擎，基于先进的创新，提供多边形惊人的图形！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >目前，游戏正在由<strong>只有一个人</strong>开发。 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >嗨，我叫尼基塔！ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >您可以在我们的Discord中与我聊天，友好的主持人将与您见面并告诉您更多关于游戏的信息:) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >我们还经常举办各种活动，您可以在游戏中获得奖励。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>沉浸在与多边形的战斗中！</strong></p>",
